 \nabla _{{\Omega _i}}^2 = \frac{1}{\sin \theta_i} \frac{\partial} {\partial \theta_i} \left( \sin \theta_i \frac{\partial}{\partial \theta_i} \right) +  \frac{1}{\sin ^ 2 \theta_i} \frac{\partial ^ 2} {\partial \varphi^2 _i}
